after your visit to occupational medicine, all prescription medicines prescribed for workers' compensation will need to be filled through our pharmacy network provider, optum. complete the optum first fill information [pdf] form to fill your prescription and provide it to the pharmacy when you pick up your prescription. reference your date of injury on the form in the format mmddyyyy. a benefit card will be mailed to you after the first fill to use with refills. this prescription plan is accepted at most major pharmacies.  for additional information contact up-leaves@sjsu.edu . university-personnel@sjsu.edu up north: 408-924-2450 up south: 408-924-2250  up webmaster up north administration building 242 up south upd building 3rd floor 